title: Skol, Associated Typographics
content:
We just released another typeface, Skol. It is a typographic stencil. Hope you like and thanks.  
 [http://associatedtypographics.com](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415034030/http:/associatedtypographics.com/ "http://associatedtypographics.com")

comments.content: PS. The 'image breaks' are because I took some showings and made something so it was easier to see on typophile. Normally those images are split.
